{
  "stem": "6736.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by-- we had breakfast. 9 o'clock in the morning, we will start school, Hebrew school in Talmud Torah.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was there from 9 to 12.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From 12 to 1, we went home to have, uh, our major meal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's like dinner.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then from 1 to 4, we took Polish, history, arithmetic, the regular schools.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at 4 o'clock, we only had time to grab a piece of chocolate or coffee or chocolate milk, and we went again to the same Hebrew school as we were in the morning.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And from there we were from 4 to 6. 6 o'clock, I would normally get sometimes $0.05, five groszy or 10 groszy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It all depends what I would get.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We would stop by in the milk store, and we would buy a sandwich.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "For $0.05 I used to get a roll and butter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And if I had $0.10, I used to get a piece of herring too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then with that, we will go to a synagogue on [NON-ENGLISH] Street, that's the Belzer synagogue.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And over there, we will pray and we will do our homework.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because at home it was very hard to do homework.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "First, the lighting was not good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in that synagogue, we will-- we had some elderly people who took a liking to our studying.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That they will sometimes buy a chocolate or some candies that they will study with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was 14 years old when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I strongly believe that if one day I should not put on my tefillin, that either my hand will fall off or something terrible will happen to my parents.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's how strict religious I was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Were both sides of your family religious, both your parents?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
